description:
Reminder that Summer Vengeance for Season 10 is NOT over yet. We will put updates for the finals up in the next coupld of weeks. Today we Start Season 11.
Holly "The Hitman" Heart took some time off but she's back to year kick ass and take names. The only problem is, her first match back is with one of our biggest, strongest girls, Rilynn Rae. Rilynn Rae has yet to win a match but we haven't been very nice to her with the opponents we've been giving her. Even today we aren't very nice to her. We give her Holly Heart, who's taken off some time from wrestling to become domesticated. She has more experience than Rilynn but Rilynn's cardio could be her key to victory over Heart.
Holly Heart gets worn down and Rilynn is able to catch up on points but will it be enough to get her her first victory today? Loser is Brutally fucked and tortured with tickles until she concedes that the winner is better at everything! Total Domination!
title: The Hitman is back in Season 11 to take on the Rattler. Barefoot style
